name: Moon Conquest (David Winsen)
description:
Play as a guy on his journey to the moon. Conquer the overweight spaceship, kick every other passengers off the ship, and go to the moon!

This game was made in under 1 week for submission to Blackthornprod Game Jam 2021. (Might contain some bugs or glitches)

NOTES: The proven working browser is Google Chrome. If you don't use chrome, or if you don't want to download chrome, then the alternative would be to download the game for Windows version.
